[Guest]: Yeah, it is very weird. I mean, it just you know, when you can't look into the other person's eye

02:00:11.240 --> 02:00:16.280
[Guest]: while talking or generally have someone in the room around you, it's just, and you know, even

02:00:16.280 --> 02:00:20.440
[Guest]: when you're looking into the other person's eye digitally, it's just not the same.

